  <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲國際性比賽佳作者，獎勵加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>15</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲全國性或地區性比賽前三名者，獎勵加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>5</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲全國性或地區性比賽佳作者，獎勵加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲教育部學術獎勵加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>15</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>6.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲國科會傑出研究獎勵加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>10</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US>7.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲國家及獎勵加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>10</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span> </p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:7.55pt;text-indent:-7.55pt'><span
  lang=EN-US>8.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>榮獲教育部國科會論文競賽優等加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>5</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分，佳作加</span><span
  lang=EN-US>3</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分。</span><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></p>
